Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇历2018年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逐步称霸世界的  神圣布列塔尼亚帝国的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个恐怖分子复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用从迷之少女C.C.处获得的绝对遵从的力量「Geass」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero决心再度发起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从沦为殖民地Area11的日本开始泛起的涟漪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给这个时代以及人们内心留下点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没有人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}Turn 02\N日本独立计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先行突入的机情局呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没联系上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chaff的浓度应该已经下降了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}（chaff：防雷达箔条）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四侦察局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据推测为黑色骑士团的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然据守在巴比伦塔内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌方拥有Knightmare Frame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  让第七特装师团从下方突进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了  快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再撑多一会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到Zero掌握这里的构造为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会前往援护的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我就是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了日本人  利用了你的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道要保护这种人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  我要送你归西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输给了过去的自己和朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后被那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭送到了布列塔尼亚皇帝面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原第十七皇位继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修·Vi·布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了啊  吾儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你使用Geass的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕属下斗胆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  恳请让属下加入帝国最强的十二骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,357)\fs23}Knight of Rounds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆桌骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想获取  抓住Zero的奖赏么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要从内部改变这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出卖朋友来出人头地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  刚才的回答甚合吾意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我在此任命Knight of Rounds
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住Zero的左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为王子却竖起反旗的不孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还有利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改写你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为Zero的事  玛丽安娜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有娜娜莉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…Geass？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却一切  做回普通人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  又想从我这里夺走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲  甚至娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理·Di·布列塔尼亚  与你刻印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的虚伪记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赋予那个男人Geass的人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想搜寻你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在黑色骑士团也已处于溃灭状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟迪特哈尔特一起逃到中华联邦去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人并不知道Zero的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪不知道娜娜莉的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出赋予皇帝Geass的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然有个妹妹  但却是没有弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  是布列塔尼亚军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找我哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有了建筑物的构造图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有识别号码的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是用不了这架Knight Mare吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的  在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那衣服  是学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是军人吗  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来帮忙治疗这个人的伤势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机密情报局的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下的直属部队  到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  如情报所示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡纳雷斯军并不知道我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人的数据还值得利用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个幸存者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的Knight Mare交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:07:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别号码是QR5-YK1D6
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说发动Geass必须直视对方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被不老不死的魔女说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在反击？  恐怖分子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是俘获了我军的Knight Mare
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但敌方人数不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必  你到底也是客将  暂处此地而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里该由身为总督的我前去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华料理的调料不合我口味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也是个不错的活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「狩人」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧  布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的好  Q1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来到21层去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P4  封锁楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R5  左边30度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N1  从那边50米处向天花板齐射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奥卿  通信中断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更改IFF的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}（IFF  敌我识别系统）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第五次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔蒂斯队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  到底是谁在指挥着恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总督…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到Zero的真实身份会是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  到底气度不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步兵部队  Zero夺走的SutherLand还有残存
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乘上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有Zero在就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹会产生  会产生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群恐怖分子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候到卡纳雷斯总督登场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来进行得很顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华莲  不是让你去21层了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才能两人独处了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Area11的诱饵好像被谁钓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是C.C.吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到这里来的即使是圆桌骑士  你还是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连修奈泽尔他们  也不知道这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚感荣幸  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为何让属下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆桌骑士中只有你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero的真实身份和Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…神殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是为毁灭神而存在的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称为「虚空之剑」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(351,361)\fs23}Akasha
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在神根岛抛弃了Zero的你  有何话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  你一直在骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说  Zero其实是你同班同学的事么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  Geass的力量这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  你对我也用过Geass吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪曲我的内心  让我服从你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心是属于你自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Zero的忠诚和仰慕都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华莲  你应该感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己决定的  自己选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了  我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  即使沦为奴隶也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我相信的是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你这身打扮打算穿到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看  变态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种口吻对Zero说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是对鲁路修说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布列塔尼亚派来援军了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量非常惊人  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四特装  开始降落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让中华联邦见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下的威严
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们神圣布列塔尼亚帝国的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也来了  这样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  应该是卡纳雷斯总督出现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃脱很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波突击部队  J层压制完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团所剩下的逃脱路线只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那里却有我们的主力部队镇守着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要把他们逼出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备安排报道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子最适合公开处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人应该已经确信自己的获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件已趋成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差你那边的楼层了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟以内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就凭当前的部署也可以死守到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪特哈尔特的装置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统还能运作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都按作战计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是B2  发现一架敌方Knight Mare
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:12:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  刚才还…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B2  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人解除IFF了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  这里是P6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人  敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是R5  R1被击破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  这样下去会来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  你一个人先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我们就是佯攻  不过是弃子作战而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了  卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着弃車保帅的念头是赢不了布列塔尼亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  物资搬运口对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到这一层来  那里是捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是基于Lancelot的量产试作机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  但现在还不是捕获的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么会跑到这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  「消失了」是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.  你那边的楼层还没完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你慌什么啊  那边不是有华莲和卜部在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙吗  「意外因素」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:15:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是朱雀  战略怎能被战术所击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身战的话我们占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是物理性的东西  是别的什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  你的真实身份是不是学生都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不能弃車保帅」这句话我相信不是虚言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  拉克夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你把日本民众拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四圣剑绝可不是浪得虚名的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是瞬间移动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必须下定决心才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备就绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部  你所争取来的这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝没有白费
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的恐怖分子  没想到会自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没文化的愚猴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机失踪  全机失去通信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别变更为异常等级C
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从截断处上升到1500后  开始回旋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这样就能把上面的敌人打向地面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错就错在你缩短了逃脱路线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这就等于  把你的所在地告诉了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了  卡纳雷斯总督
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督被干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科恩威尔卿在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和总督一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那指挥系统呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要交给内务省的文官？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是惊慌失措的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是夺权  只是临时措施
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾公主殿下之名起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们能合作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说柯内莉亚公主殿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就前往现场指挥救援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔弗烈德负责警察那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是  Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…喂喂  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Zero吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  怎么突然间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  真的是本人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人啊  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止播放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  信号不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我设置的Ω线路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,360)\fs23}Line Omega
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这个的人只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁开眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有拥有力量的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争与歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣扬的  强者的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续着错误  不断流传的悲喜剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界没有任何的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不得不复活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要强者还在继续欺凌弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会继续反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是愚蠢的卡纳雷斯总督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才  我已施以「天诛」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  突然间就行动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11区的国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  发信源是中华联邦总领事馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华联邦的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是流亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样突破包围网的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们从倒塌的大楼里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以巴比伦塔作为通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  中华联邦是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先商量好了的？  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  Zero不是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个就是冒牌货了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  只要突入总领事馆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重大的违规行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会引发国际问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然自称Zero  也就是杀害皇族的犯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和EU作战也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边都会  深陷泥潭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害总督和确保逃脱路线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然同时实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份智慧和胆识
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Zero  本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与所有行使错误力量的人们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  我在此再次宣布\N成立「日本合众国」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本还没有奉天子谕旨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我的决定有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero啊  只要是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「合众国…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…日本」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子建国？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间房间将成为日本合众国的第一块领土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一间房间的国家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还依旧是个有趣的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分人种、主义与宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为国民的条件只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是施行正义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前就是我中华联邦的领土了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日后外交桌上见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底能有多少利用价值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是布列塔尼亚军的话  已经让他们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你是Zero的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  是哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对猜谜没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想知道而已  真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我来要Zero的命了


